nodes.text: Doctor Aphra 13 is the upcoming thirteenth  issue of the canon comic series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra, and is part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event. The issue will be written by Alyssa Wong, illustrated by Minkyu Jung, and published by Marvel Comics on August 25, 2021.
